text: Muri AG railway station () is a railway station in the municipality of Muri, in the Swiss canton of Aargau. It is an intermediate stop on the standard gauge Rupperswil–Immensee line of Swiss Federal Railways. ==Services== The following services stop at Muri AG: * Zürich S-Bahn : rush-hour service to Zürich Hauptbahnhof. * Aargau S-Bahn: ** : hourly service to . ** : half- hourly service between and , with every other train continuing from Lenzburg to . == References == == External links == * * Category:Railway stations in the canton of Aargau Category:Swiss Federal Railways stations
